				At level 14, it does a maximum of 29 HP of damage to all monsters in the &quot;radius of effect&quot;.<BR>
<BR>
I'm not a big fan of this spell because it costs so much mana.  But it is nice if you are helping someone out who has been mobbed by a group of monsters.  Heal the victim, then cast the word of pain, and that should tilt the balance of power in your friend's favor.
