				This is not a good spell, sometimes if you are in a group and yoiu have alot of lower level monsters on your group it is okay. But it has been my experiance that if you are fighting more than one if you cast this you will draw creatures to you leaving you unable heal. Also if you cast this in dungeons you will pull  everything close to your group onto you. I was in splitpaw awhile back and had 3 gnoll shaman on our group i casted the spell and pulled 2 snakes and three low level gnolls to the group and the 2 other shaman turned on me needless to say we died that day hehe.<BR>
Also this spell is worthless when you are soloing because it takes to long for me to cast. With one creature you can cast it but 2 or more you cant get it off, and its not efficient for just one creatue. I quit using the spell maybe when i get higher level I will try it again ?<BR>

