	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I've found this to be a wonderful attack spell, when used in the right situation.  While it is fairly worthless while soloing, it's very valuable to a group.  First, if you can hit multiple opponents, the damage to mana ratio is better than other cleric attack spells.  Second, if the fight is getting rough for one or more of your party members, Word of Pain will get the monsters' attention on you and spread out the damage the party is receiving.  But never ever use near a dungeon wall, that's the easiest way to get yourself killed.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
